data.title: Typical Quizno's, but they don't take Quizno's coupons any more
data.text:
This downtown Sacramento Quizno's is one I have been to many times over the past few years. They offer the usual Quizno's fare of toasted sandwiches, so if you like it anywhere, you'll like it here too. They do a fine job.

My disappointment on my most recent visit was a sign announcing that this location no longer accepts coupons. (You can get these by signing up for Quizno's promotional emails.) The coupon says "participating locations", which this one used to be. But no more. So if that matters to you, well, there you are.
